@mattip I'm not sure there is anything to expose here, unless we'd want to properly expose the entire `numpy.typing` tesing suite?

All this PR does is taking a set of comments and formatting them (when applicable), thus allowing us to use aliases.
It doesn't touch `mypy` itself or its output.

